<body style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;">
  <%- include('./partials/nav') %>

  <div class="container my-5" style="max-width: 800px;">
    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4 text-dark text-center">📖 About SnipSnap</h2>

    <p class="text-secondary" style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      SnipSnap is a modern, lightweight, and user-friendly blogging platform designed to make writing and sharing thoughts accessible to everyone.
      Whether you're a student, developer, writer, or enthusiast, SnipSnap helps you express your ideas, tell stories, or post tutorials in a clean and distraction-free environment.
    </p>

    <p class="text-secondary mt-4" style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      Founded with simplicity and creativity in mind, SnipSnap encourages open sharing and community engagement. No unnecessary clutter—just your content, your words, your space.
    </p>

    <p class="text-secondary mt-4" style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      We’re committed to continuous improvement and introducing more useful features like blog editing, inline images, social sharing, and more.
      If you have ideas or feedback, don’t hesitate to <a href="/contact" class="text-decoration-none fw-semibold">reach out to us</a>.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-5 text-center">
      <p class="fw-bold text-dark mb-1">💡 Built with ❤️ by Aman Show</p>
      <p class="text-muted">Powered by Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and Bootstrap</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include('./partials/scripts') %>
  <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
